    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. While it runs well, the car does show its age with several noticeable exterior scratches, a few small dings on the passenger side, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some minor staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster, but all electronics and climate controls remain fully functional. It is a solid choice for someone who prioritizes mechanical reliability over cosmetic perfection.",
