    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are honored to present this superlative vehicle, preserved in showroom condition. This specimen represents the pinnacle of automotive maintenance, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory character. Every component has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to confirm its mechanical perfection and aesthetic purity. For the discerning buyer seeking an investment-grade vehicle that transcends the typical secondary market offering, this automobile stands as a definitive benchmark of quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
