    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This is a rare find for a discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating and absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather still retains its factory scent, and every surface\u2014from the steering wheel to the bolsters\u2014is free of wear or creases. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line, with a comprehensive, preventative service history fully documented at the dealership. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every inch of this car reflects a standard of care that is impossible to replicate. It is, quite simply, the finest example of this model currently available on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
